{"tid":404713,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得自己唔識考試","createTime":"2017-09-18T10:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T03:24:41.000Z","uid":106745,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7ae2682b567dfd0fc74e42abdf02b05ac7df09a","tid":404713,"uid":106745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:14:16.000Z","msg":"今年final yr啦<br />\n由中學考試考到而家 <br />\n係到呢幾年先發現自己唔撚識考試<br />\n<br />\n個時dse低分求鳩其入左啲水泡<br />\n開頭都叫努力下都過到三 點知愈讀gpa就愈爛<br />\n諗住可能hea底讀唔熟書啦<br />\n咁之後都有認真讀<br />\n點知有科係同一班人做proj assignment <br />\n明明啲分都一樣 係出嚟個garde我就B 佢地就B+<br />\n<br />\n有時都係到諗 究竟我係未夠勤力 定係唔識考試<br />\n定真係份人蠢 温極錯野又答錯野咁<br />\n身邊啲人個個爆seed謝要追Hon<br />\n我自己就扮曬野同人地講grad到就得啦 使撚追hon<br />\n但其實係怕自己爆完seed後都考到成舊屎<br />\n到時真係唔認自己蠢都唔得<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4766fccc3e80a1877d07dfb50b8fa707ea1a040d","tid":404713,"uid":31752,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:16:02.000Z","msg":"廢咪廢乜野唔識考試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe0ff79ceb5a122034f772473f190cf0ce7849c","tid":404713,"uid":106745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:22:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢咪廢乜野唔識考試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌巴打你咁撚直接"},{"pid":"2307f6486200b27d709c0d72e7e09592a9d99403","tid":404713,"uid":106745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa0a15f1b1faa1d24bc91877a7ce605d9a374c9","tid":404713,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:37:32.000Z","msg":"考試有技巧是真的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識技巧得死背 2.2grad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b31c6ee6c0bb1fb842bda3aa94538f3b490bfb3","tid":404713,"uid":106745,"